================================================================================
Architectural inspiration
================================================================================

The theming engine architecture (IThemeService + ThemeRevision pattern,
ResourceDictionary swap, design tokens, semantic brush layering) is inspired
by the internal theming of Heimdall.Next (https://github.com/jbombled/Heimdall.Next),
authored by the same person. No source code from Heimdall.Next is copied
into this repository ; only the pattern is reused.
